room_title: Escape room "The Quest" by Escape Goat in Orlando
room_address: 1165 E Plant St, Winter Garden, FL 34787
room_description: In the serene and tranquil village of Oakenshire, devastation looms on your horizon. A great Garzon dragon has wrecked havoc across your lands. You find yourself, as volunteers on a quest for Oakenshire, standing at the door of Lord Montague; the man in the mountain most known for his studies of magical creatures. He perhaps possesses the key to your survival.
